OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772012416
OL,3,CMan jailed for seven years for non-
OL,4,Ccontact child sex offences
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after
OL,7,Fblackmailing children into sending
OL,8,Findecent images of themselves.
OL,10,FManchester Crown Court heard how Ryan
OL,11,FGreenhow, 37, committed the offences
OL,12,Fbetween November 2024 and March 2025
OL,13,Fand involved him contacting six
OL,14,Fvictims via social media platforms
OL,15,Fincluding WhatsApp, TikTok and
OL,16,FSnapchat. Greenhow then blackmailed
OL,17,Fthe victims into sending him indecent
OL,18,Fimage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
