OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772012416
OL,3,CMan jailed for seven years for non-
OL,4,Ccontact child sex offences
OL,6,FHe would send the victims, aged
OL,7,Fbetween 12-15, an indecent image,
OL,8,Fmaking claims that the image depicted
OL,9,Fthem when it was a picture of a naked
OL,10,Fwoman obtained from the internet, and
OL,11,Fthreatened to send the image to their
OL,12,Ffriends and family if the victims did
OL,13,Fnot do as Greenhow said.
OL,15,FThis led to him making demands for
OL,16,Findecent images from victims located
OL,17,Fin areas across Greater Manchester,
OL,18,FLancashire and Buckinghamshire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772012416
OL,3,CMan jailed for seven years for non-
OL,4,Ccontact child sex offences
OL,6,FGreenhow would then send numerous text
OL,7,Fmessages threatening his victims,
OL,8,Fincluding saying "This is your last
OL,9,Fchance, everyone will know this is
OL,10,Fyou" and "I have seen your nudes, add
OL,11,Fme".
OL,13,FOn some occasions the victim would
OL,14,Frespond and say that she did not know
OL,15,Fwhat they were talking about, but kept
OL,16,Freceiving messages telling them that
OL,17,Fit was their "last chance".
OL,26,@pD@ROUrD@DO]rD@JOUsD@CO]yD@NOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
