OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772012416
OL,3,CMan jailed for seven years for non-
OL,4,Ccontact child sex offences
OL,6,FSome of the victims did send Greenhow
OL,7,Fimages and reported his activity to
OL,8,Ftheir parents, carers and school
OL,9,Fteachers.
OL,11,FGreenhow pleaded guilty to 22 counts
OL,12,Fof non-contact child sex offences
OL,13,Fincluding child sexual exploitation,
OL,14,Fsharing images or film to cause alarm,
OL,15,Fcausing or inciting a child aged under
OL,16,F16 to engage in sexual activity and
OL,17,Fmalicious communications at an earlier
OL,18,Fhearing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
