OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772012416
OL,3,CMan jailed for seven years for non-
OL,4,Ccontact child sex offences
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to seven years and
OL,7,Ffour months in prison at Manchester
OL,8,FCrown Court on Tuesday 24 February.
OL,10,FAccording to Greater Manchester Police
OL,11,F(GMP) between April 2023 and May 2025,
OL,12,FSnapchat was identified as being the
OL,13,Fbiggest social media platform involved
OL,14,Fin cases, with it being involved 61%
OL,15,Fof the time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772012416
OL,3,CMan jailed for seven years for non-
OL,4,Ccontact child sex offences
OL,6,FStrangers not known to the victim
OL,7,Faccount for almost half (49%) of
OL,8,Fonline offenders, with 22% of all our
OL,9,Fchild sexual abuse offences within GM
OL,10,Fin 2023/2024 being online, which is
OL,11,Fslightly above the national picture of
OL,12,F20% being online.
OL,14,FDetective Constable Adair, of our City
OL,15,Fof Manchester Division, said:
OL,16,F"Firstly, I would like to thank the
OL,17,Fvictims in this case for coming
OL,18,Fforward, reporting their ordeal to the
OL,19,Fpolice and allowing us to investigate,
OL,20,Fresulting in today's sentencing.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772012416
OL,3,CMan jailed for seven years for non-
OL,4,Ccontact child sex offences
OL,6,F"Greenhow used several different
OL,7,Fsocial media platforms pretending to
OL,8,Fbe a 15-year-old boy and followed the
OL,9,Fsame method with each of his victims `
OL,10,Fsending them random images obtained
OL,11,Ffrom the internet, falsely attributing
OL,12,Fthem to the victim, then threatening
OL,13,Fto share the image with the victim's
OL,14,Ffriends and family in exchange for an
OL,15,Findecent image of the victim.
OL,17,F"Once our investigation was underway,
OL,18,Fdetailed phone analysis led to us
OL,19,Fidentifying further victims. Officers
OL,20,Fworked to safeguard these victims from
OL,21,Fany further harm.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
