CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772012416
OL,3,CMan jailed for seven years for non-
OL,4,Ccontact child sex offences
OL,6,F"This sentencing is part of our wider
OL,7,Fwork to tackle child sexual
OL,8,Fexploitation and we're committed to
OL,9,Fprotecting victims and bringing
OL,10,Foffenders to justice.
OL,12,F"Anybody who thinks they may have been
OL,13,Fa victim of sexual abuse can contact
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police at any time.
OL,15,FWe will provide support, conduct
OL,16,Fthorough investigations, and take firm
OL,17,Faction against offenders. Your
OL,18,Fallegations will be taken seriously,
OL,19,Fand you will be treated with dignity
OL,20,Fand respect.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
